Maid: Since there are few maids,
cleaning is quite difficult...

Maid: The vase was broken... I wonder
who the culprit is...

Rabi: W-Who could it be! I won't forgive
them!

Maid: Since the castle knights are
currently away, let's clean the areas
that we usually can't clean.

Lala: You can even snoop around in
private.

Maid: Since there are few maids,
cleaning is quite difficult...

Zerachiel: Maybe because it's a small
castle?

Claudia: That might be true, but it
could also be about wanting to work in
the Demon Lord's castle for the cleaning
job.
Claudia: Normally, I would be scared.

Maid: The damage to the town was beyond
comparison to that of the castle. I also
lost a friend.

Maid: ...If I hadn't been in the castle,
would I have died too?

Megildin: My dear comrades of the
magical continent.

Megildin: And, our esteemed guests who
will assist us.

Megildin: I express my heartfelt
gratitude for gathering here for the
sake of justice.

Megildin: This attack was the result of
my incompetence.

Megildin: First of all, I would like to
deeply apologize.

Megildin: Due to the previous angel
attack, our Val has suffered devastating
damage.

Megildin: Peace has been lost along with
many lives, and the people are truly
ruled by fear.

Megildin: The actions of the angels are
by no means forgivable.

Megildin: I deeply engrave the feelings
and lives of those whose lives were
tragically taken...

Megildin: We must unite and stand
against the Star God.
Megildin: It will be a difficult battle.

Megildin: However, no matter what crisis
may come, I believe that all of you can
overcome it.

Megildin: Because we are heroes standing
on this earth.

Megildin: There may be those who will
perish.

Megildin: There may be those who will
perish.

Megildin: However, it is engraved in my
heart.

Megildin: I am grateful to have been
with all of you noble heroes.

Megildin: I will send myself to the
battlefield... to resent the incompetent
king.

Megildin: I promise to carry the will of
countless heroic spirits and carve out
the future.
Megildin: Please, lend me your strength.

Megildin: Together, let's regain peace
and walk towards the stolen tomorrow.

Megildin: Everyone, we will now head
towards the sanctuary.

Megildin: We will capture the
Transference Gate Absorb Gate and
attempt to reclaim the Seventh Curse.

Megildin: I heard that the Seventh Curse
is said to be dormant within a certain
girl.

Megildin: This is Lady Effy, the saint
of the Orpheus Sect.

Megildin: In order to save Lady Effy, I
ask for the assistance of all members of
the Orpheus Sect.

Megildin: And the heroes who protected
Vaal in the previous attack will also
lend their assistance.

Megildin: Everyone, now is the time to
join forces.

Megildin: All troops, head towards the
sanctuary.

Megildin: We will show our true power to
the Star God!
